### CCR-026 — BS-04-05 Deck Registration (AT-05)
###
### 검증:
### - POST /decks 저장 (54장 매핑)
### - 중복 UID 거부
### - GET /decks 목록
### - PATCH /tables/{id}/active_deck
### - DeckRegistered WebSocket 이벤트
###
### Schema 정정 (2026-05-11, S9 Cycle 2 — Type D drift):
###   request field: "deck_name" → "name"
###   response field: "deck_id" → "id"; "card_count" → "cardsRegistered" (camelCase)
###   response field: "created_at" → "createdAt"
###   초기 응답 status = "registering" (async card add 가능성. 추후 PATCH 또는 후속
###   POST /decks/{id}/cards 필요할 수 있음 — team2 확인 대상)
### 근거: 실제 BO 응답 (POST /api/v1/decks 201) — 2026-05-11 S9 cycle 2 실행 검증

@host = http://localhost:18001
@admin_token = {{$dotenv ADMIN_JWT}}

### 50.1 POST /api/v1/decks — deck 생성 (실행 검증됨 2026-05-11)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/decks
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "WSOP-FT-2026-Deck-01",
  "cards": [
    { "uid": "04A3B2C1D001", "rank": 12, "suit": 0 },
    { "uid": "04A3B2C1D002", "rank": 11, "suit": 0 },
    { "uid": "04A3B2C1D003", "rank": 10, "suit": 0 },
    { "uid": "04A3B2C1D004", "rank": 9,  "suit": 0 },
    { "uid": "04A3B2C1D005", "rank": 8,  "suit": 0 }
  ]
}

# (52장 + Joker 2 = 54장 전체 전송. 간결화 위해 5장만 표시)
#
# 실제 응답: 201 Created
# {
#   "id": "a32edc46-4016-4834-b491-6096ebbccd8b",     // UUID (envelope 없음)
#   "name": "WSOP-FT-2026-Deck-01",
#   "status": "registering",
#   "createdAt": "2026-05-11T09:39:48.647245Z",
#   "notes": null,
#   "cardsRegistered": 0                              // 초기값 0 — async 가능
# }
#
# Drift 후속 검증 항목 (team2 확인 요구):
#   - cardsRegistered 가 0 이면 어떤 후속 호출로 cards 적재되는가?
#   - status "registering" → "ready" 전이 endpoint는?

### 50.2 POST /api/v1/decks/{id}/cards — 중복 UID (DRIFT-50.2 회귀 방지)
###
### 갱신 (2026-05-12, S7 Cycle 5 — DRIFT-50.2 dup-uid 422 fix):
###   이전 시나리오는 obsolete 단일 POST /decks 에 cards 배열 — 현 API 는
###   POST /decks (name 만) → POST /decks/{id}/cards (one-by-one). 422 정합.
### Issue: #282
###
### Step 1 — deck 생성 + 첫 카드 등록 (UID = 04A3B2C1D001)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/decks
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "drift-50-2-dup-test" }

# 예상: 201 Created — { id, name, status: "registering", cardsRegistered: 0 }
# id 를 dup_deck_id 로 보존 (REST Client `@dup_deck_id = ...`)

###
POST {{host}}/api/v1/decks/{{dup_deck_id}}/cards
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "cardCode": "AS", "rfidUid": "04A3B2C1D001" }

# 예상: 201 Created — cardCode "AS" 등록

###
### Step 2 — 같은 deck 에 다른 cardCode 로 동일 UID 재등록 (DRIFT-50.2 핵심)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/decks/{{dup_deck_id}}/cards
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "cardCode": "KS", "rfidUid": "04A3B2C1D001" }

# 예상: 422 Unprocessable Entity (DRIFT-50.2 정합 — 이전 코드는 409 반환)
# {
#   "detail": {
#     "code": "DUPLICATE_UID",
#     "uid": "04A3B2C1D001",
#     "existing_deck_id": "{{dup_deck_id}}",
#     "existing_card_code": "AS",
#     "message": "UID already registered in another deck"
#   }
# }

###
### 50.2b POST /api/v1/decks/import — 벌크 intra-payload dup UID
###
### dict[card_code → uid] 구조의 함정: 다른 card_code 가 동일 uid 를 가지면
### dict 자체로는 차단되지 않음. 명시 검증 추가됨 (DRIFT-50.2).
POST {{host}}/api/v1/decks/import
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "intra-dup-payload-test",
  "cards": {
    "AS": "DEADBEEF01", "KS": "DEADBEEF02", "QS": "DEADBEEF03",
    "JS": "DEADBEEF04", "TS": "DEADBEEF05", "9S": "DEADBEEF06",
    "8S": "DEADBEEF07", "7S": "DEADBEEF08", "6S": "DEADBEEF09",
    "5S": "DEADBEEF0A", "4S": "DEADBEEF0B", "3S": "DEADBEEF0C",
    "2S": "DEADBEEF0D",
    "AH": "DEADBEEF0E", "KH": "DEADBEEF0F", "QH": "DEADBEEF10",
    "JH": "DEADBEEF11", "TH": "DEADBEEF12", "9H": "DEADBEEF13",
    "8H": "DEADBEEF14", "7H": "DEADBEEF15", "6H": "DEADBEEF16",
    "5H": "DEADBEEF17", "4H": "DEADBEEF18", "3H": "DEADBEEF19",
    "2H": "DEADBEEF1A",
    "AD": "DEADBEEF1B", "KD": "DEADBEEF1C", "QD": "DEADBEEF1D",
    "JD": "DEADBEEF1E", "TD": "DEADBEEF1F", "9D": "DEADBEEF20",
    "8D": "DEADBEEF21", "7D": "DEADBEEF22", "6D": "DEADBEEF23",
    "5D": "DEADBEEF24", "4D": "DEADBEEF25", "3D": "DEADBEEF26",
    "2D": "DEADBEEF27",
    "AC": "DEADBEEF28", "KC": "DEADBEEF29", "QC": "DEADBEEF2A",
    "JC": "DEADBEEF2B", "TC": "DEADBEEF2C", "9C": "DEADBEEF2D",
    "8C": "DEADBEEF2E", "7C": "DEADBEEF2F", "6C": "DEADBEEF30",
    "5C": "DEADBEEF31", "4C": "DEADBEEF32", "3C": "DEADBEEF33",
    "2C": "DEADBEEF01"
  }
}

# 예상: 422 Unprocessable Entity (intra_payload scope)
# {
#   "detail": {
#     "code": "DUPLICATE_UID",
#     "scope": "intra_payload",
#     "conflicts": [
#       { "card_code": "2C", "rfid_uid": "DEADBEEF01", "duplicate_of_card": "AS" }
#     ]
#   }
# }
# 마지막 "2C" 가 첫 "AS" 와 동일 UID — intra-payload 충돌

